data.description: Charming brick home in Skipcha Mountain, 3 Bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and over 1500 sqft. The inviting entry leads into a cozy living area with a fireplace and high ceilings. The Kitchen/dining area has a breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom with and on suite bathroom features vaulted ceilings and the on suite bath features a garden tub and separate shower. The backyard has a raised deck perfect for family gatherings. Call for more information or to schedule your showing today. NEW VINYL FLOOR INSTALLED, TAWNY OAK!!
